  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">The stagecoach which was to take this letter went by while Hervey Eliphaz Weston was watching the balloon. Warren Weston has a boarding place and left today. Hervey E. Weston relays Warren Weston&apos;s request for clothing and comments: &quot;You will think I order pretty well!&quot; Hervey E. Weston tells about the punishment meted out to a horse poisoner across the street.</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">In the postscript, Hervey E. Weston writes: &quot;Mind send a shirt or 2 Monday or Tuesday if you get 20 tailors to do it.&quot;</subfield>
